The paper discusses the robustness of kNN classifiers and classifiers that combine kNN with neural networks against adversarial examples. This topic falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer security and cryptography (cs.CR), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
